SubjectBy-elections (2) - Toronto Centre and York Centre
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of TORONTO CENTRE, Ontario, and YORK CENTRE, Ontario, with polling to take place on October 26, 2020.
